        "text": "τὸν Πατέρα Μου",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "My Father",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") Jesus even, when He is just about to drink the cup, retains that filial disposition which He had previously and always towards the Father; see ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
